{"ProductId":"23","Title":"Classic™ Wood","ShortDescription":"Enhance the natural character of your home with a handcrafted Classic™ Wood garage door","Description":"","ThumbnailImage":null,"ShowcaseImage":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/classic-wood-design-short-stockton-window-cedar-garage-door-595.webp?sfvrsn=91462566_2","CanonicalUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/classicwood","Overview":"<h3>Warmth, Character, and Versatility</h3><h4>Authentic Wood Construction</h4><p>Choose from single-layer solid wood or energy-efficient three-layer insulated options, all expertly built for strength and reliability.</p><h4>Premium Materials</h4><p>Available in sustainably sourced redwood, hemlock, or cedar, plus paint-grade Extira&reg; wood composite for a truly custom look.</p><h4>Tailored to You</h4><p>Pick from raised, recessed, or flush panel designs, with your choice of optional hand-carved windows and decorative hardware to match your home&rsquo;s style.</p><h4>Finish It Your Way</h4><p>Select a primed door, elegant white paint, or one of nine rich stains that highlight natural wood grain&mdash;or get creative with over 1,500 custom <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/colorblast\">Color Blast&reg;</a> paint colors.</p><h4>Insulation Where You Want It</h4><p>Enjoy added comfort and efficiency with <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/garage-door-materials/insulation\">polystyrene insulation</a> (R-value 5.9) on Model 33 flush panel doors.</p><h4>Built for the Elements</h4><p><a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/buyingguide/residential/windcode-residential-information\">WindCode&reg; reinforcement</a> is available for extra protection in high-wind areas.</p><h4>Environmental Assurance</h4><p>Clopay doors are compliant with environmental laws and regulations. Clopay doors do not contain HFCs. All Clopay doors are compliant with:</p><ul><li>California SB 1013</li><li>Washington HB 1112 &ndash; Hydrofluorocarbon Greenhouse Gas Emissions</li><li>Canadian regulations amending the ozone-depleting substances and halocarbon alternatives regulations</li><li>New Jersey A-5583/S-3919 &ndash; Greenhouse Gas Bill</li></ul>","Options":"","Construction":"<p>Every Classic&trade; Wood garage door is handcrafted in the USA. Depending on the model, you&rsquo;ll get either solid, single-layer wood construction or a three-layer insulated design for extra comfort and durability. Thoughtful details make maintenance simple. Plus, you&rsquo;re covered by Clopay&rsquo;s warranties&mdash;one year for construction and paint, and two years for stain&mdash;so you can feel confident in your investment.Options include:</p><h4>Model 44 Raised Panel Wood Garage Doors</h4><ul><li>1-3/8\" heavy-duty stile and rail and dowel pin construction</li><li>Handcrafted short or long raised panels in Redwood, Cedar, Hemlock (stain grade) or Extira&reg; (paint grade)</li><li>Handcrafted wood decorative windows, available in six designs</li></ul><img src=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/construction/cutaway-classic-wood-model-44.webp?sfvrsn=5ea0128d_1\" alt=\"Model 44\" sf-size=\"100\" /><ol><li>Wood Frame and Panels</li></ol><h4>Model 20/10 Recessed Panel Wood Garage Doors</h4><ul><li>Handcrafted 1-3/8\" section thickness with stile and rail construction in Hemlock</li><li>Model 20 offers Luan or Okoume panels, both available in stain grade or paint grade options.</li><li>Model 10 features paint grade Hardboard panels.</li></ul><img src=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/construction/cutaway-classic-wood-model-20-10.webp?sfvrsn=76bea457_1\" alt=\"Classic Wood\" sf-size=\"100\" /><ol><li>Wood Frame and Panels</li></ol><h4>Model 33 Flush Panel Wood Garage Doors</h4><ul><li>Three-layer construction with polystyrene insulation sandwiched between interior and exterior boards. Interior Luan backer. R-value 5.9.</li><li>Calculated garage door section R-value is in&nbsp;accordance with DASMA TDS-163.</li><li>Heavy-duty 1-5/8\" section thickness</li><li>Exterior wood options include Smooth Luan and Okoume.</li></ul><img src=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/construction/cutaway-classic-wood-model-33.webp?sfvrsn=6fe2c0b6_1\" alt=\"Model 33\" sf-size=\"100\" /><ol><li>Wood Exterior Board</li><li>Polystyrene Insulated Wood Frame</li><li>Wood Interior Board</li></ol>","Models":"","FeaturesBenefits":"","SpringsHardware":"","GroupName":"","H1HeaderTitle":"Classic Wood","DisplayIndex":20,"ImageGallery":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/image-gallery/classic-wood","ColorDisclaimer":"<p>Make your Classic&trade; Wood garage door your own with a curated selection of rich stains and paints. Each finish is designed to bring out the natural character of the wood, letting you match or accent your home&rsquo;s exterior.</p><p>Choose from nine beautiful stain options including Natural, Natural Oak, Cedar, Teak, Butternut, Mahogany, Dark Oak, Dark Oak Ebony Wash, and Ebony Wash. These stains enhance the wood&rsquo;s grain and warmth, giving you everything from light, golden tones to deep, dramatic finishes.</p><p>If you prefer a painted look, choose crisp white for a timeless, clean appearance that works with almost any style. For even more personalization, Clopay offers over 1,500 custom<a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/colorblast\"> Color Blast&reg; paint options</a>, so you can find the best shade to complement your home.</p>","TopSectionDisclaimer":"<p>With your Classic™ Wood door each model offers a variety of top section options, so you can tailor your door’s look to your taste.</p>\r\n<ul><li>Model 44: Go for solid panels for a clean, understated style, or add windows in designs like Stockton, Cathedral, Sherwood, or Horizon to brighten up your garage and boost visual interest. Short and long configurations are available to match your door’s panel style.</li>\r\n<li>Model 20 & 10: Enjoy the same flexibility, with solid or windowed top sections (including Stockton, Cathedral, Horizon, and Sherwood styles), available in both short and long versions.</li>\r\n<li>Model 33: Choose from plain short or long top sections for a streamlined, modern finish.</li>\r\n","HardwareDisclaimer":"","DesignDisclaimer":"","RelatedProducts":[{"Title":"Modern Steel™","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/modern-steel-flush_fullview-window-black-garage-door-595.webp?sfvrsn=db7014e9_14","Id":"170","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/modern-steel-collection","DisplayIndex":7,"ShortDescription":"Subtle modern beauty, simple up-keep","AlternativeText":"Modern Steel"},{"Title":"Avante<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> – Now Available with C-Power™ Technology","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/tnahcpower01showcase.webp?sfvrsn=e1a1ed6c_1","Id":"16","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/avante","DisplayIndex":9,"ShortDescription":"Aluminum and glass doors that make your garage a stunning focal point, providing natural light by day and a dramatic glow at night","AlternativeText":"Avante"},{"Title":"Classic™ Steel","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/classicsteel-ironoreshowcase.webp?sfvrsn=25b7a514_1","Id":"13","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/classic","DisplayIndex":19,"ShortDescription":"Strength and durability in a wide range of looks and colors, so you never have to sacrifice style","AlternativeText":"Classic Steel"}],"ProductBrochures":[{"Title":"Wood Idea Book","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/brochures/rsdr-woodidea-10.webp?sfvrsn=e62fe2df_5","Type":"Brochure","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/RSDR-WOODIDEA-10.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":1}],"ProductInstallationAndCare":[{"Title":"Installation Instructions for Wood Garage Doors",